##-------------------------------------------------------------------##
The code used to implement the sniffer IEEE 802.15.4 and the programs could be founded in : 

[1] Bloessl, B.; Leitner, C.; Dressler, F.; Sommer, C. A GNU Radio-based IEEE 802.15.4 Testbed.  IEEE, 2003

[2] https://www.wime-project.net/installation/

[3] https://www.gnuradio.org/

We use the PyBombs method to perform the installation of the software and modules.

For the firmware, we use the instructions detailled in :

[4] https://kb.ettus.com/Building_and_Installing_the_USRP_Open-Source_Toolchain_(UHD_and_GNU_Radio)_on_Linux


